      • customColocalise

        public CustomColoc2.ColocResult<T> customColocalise(Img<T> image1,
                                                    Img<T> image2,
                                                    Coloc_2.BoundingBox roi,
                                                    Img<T> mask,
                                                    List<ResultHandler<T>> extraHandlers)
                                             throws MissingPreconditionException
        Call this method to run a whole colocalisation configuration, all selected algorithms get run on the supplied images. You can specify the data further by supplying appropriate information in the mask structure.
        Parameters:
        image1 - First image.
        image2 - Second image.
        roi - Region of interest to which analysis is confined.
        mask - Mask to which analysis is confined.
        extraHandlers - additional objects to be notified of analysis results.
        Returns:
        Data structure housing the results.
        Throws:
        MissingPreconditionException
